'''薑黃'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Curcuma longa}}''），又稱'''寶鼎香'''，為[[薑科|薑科]][[薑黃屬|薑黃屬]]植物，在一些亞洲國家稱作turmeric或kunyit。其根莖所磨成的深黃色粉末為[[咖哩|咖哩]]的主要成份之一，也用在[[南洋|南洋]][[料理|料理]]，嚐起來味苦而辛，帶點土味。主成分[[薑黃素|薑黃素]]（{{lang|la|curcumin}}）具有一些醫療保健的效果，因此薑黃也出現在[[中醫|中醫]]藥材中。<ref name=eddm>{{cite journal |last= Chan |first= E.W.C. ''et al.'' |title= Effects of different drying methods on the antioxidant properties of leaves and tea of ginger species |journal= Food Chemistry |volume= 113 |issue= 1 |pages= 166–172 |year= 2009 |doi= 10.1016/j.foodchem.2008.07.090 |last2= Lim |first2= Y.Y. |last3= Wong |first3= S.K. |last4= Lim |first4= K.K. |last5= Tan |first5= S.P. |last6= Lianto |first6= F.S. |last7= Yong |first7= M.Y. }}</ref><ref name="#1">Materia Indica, 1826, [[Whitelaw_Ainslie|Whitelaw Ainslie]], M.D. M.R.A.S., via Google Books</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Indian Spices|title=Turmeric processing|date=|url=http://kaubic.in/spicesdatabase/Turmeric/processing.htm|work=kaubic.in|publisher=|accessdate=2013-07-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528120654/http://kaubic.in/spicesdatabase/Turmeric/processing.htm|archivedate=2013-05-28}}</ref><ref name=nag>{{cite journal |author= Nagpal M, Sood S |title= Role of curcumin in systemic and oral health: An overview |url= |journal= J Nat Sci Biol Med |volume= 4|issue= 1 | pages=3–7  |year=2013 |pmid= 23633828 |pmc=3633300 |doi=10.4103/0976-9668.107253 }}</ref>

